## 🔍 creating and setting password for  devops user account

> **Timestamp:** `2026-06-11 10:41:29`

### 01. `sudo useradd -m -s /bin/bash -c "Devops User" devops-user && sudo passwd devops-user`

```bash
sudo useradd -m -s /bin/bash -c "Devops User" devops-user && sudo passwd devops-user
```

