## 🔍 adding devops-user to sudo group with full passwordless sudo privileges configuration

> **Timestamp:** `2026-06-11 12:02:15`

### 01. `sudo usermod -aG sudo devops-user && echo "devops-user ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL" | sudo tee /etc/sudoers.d/devops-user && sudo chmod 440 /etc/sudoers.d/devops-user`

```bash
sudo usermod -aG sudo devops-user && echo "devops-user ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL" | sudo tee /etc/sudoers.d/devops-user && sudo chmod 440 /etc/sudoers.d/devops-user
```

**Output:**

```text
devops-user ALL=(ALL) NOPASSWD: ALL
```


