## 🔍 Verifying devops-user account

> **Timestamp:** `2026-06-13 08:31:07`

### 01. `id devops-user`

```bash
id devops-user
```

**Output:**

```text
uid=1001(devops-user) gid=1001(devops-user) groups=1001(devops-user),27(sudo)
```

### 02. `grep devops-user /etc/passwd`

```bash
grep devops-user /etc/passwd
```

**Output:**

```text
devops-user:x:1001:1001:Devops User:/home/devops-user:/bin/bash
```

### 03. `groups devops-user`

```bash
groups devops-user
```

**Output:**

```text
devops-user : devops-user sudo
```

### 04. `sudo -u devops-user whoami`

```bash
sudo -u devops-user whoami
```

**Output:**

```text
devops-user
```

### 05. `sudo -u devops-user id`

```bash
sudo -u devops-user id
```

**Output:**

```text
uid=1001(devops-user) gid=1001(devops-user) groups=1001(devops-user),27(sudo)
```

